"这是第三次 也是最后一次 我给你写信了
"This is the third and last time I will write to you.

585
01:02:35,250 --> 01:02:37,550
如果你中午时 仍然还在...
If you are still here at noon...

586
01:02:37,620 --> 01:02:40,710
我警告你 你将受到毁灭性的打击
I warn you, you will hear from me to your very great destruction.

587
01:02:40,790 --> 01:02:43,310
请尽快回复"
Please give me your answer speedily. "

588
01:02:44,230 --> 01:02:45,660
去你妈的!
Go fuck yourself!

589
