他们说会考虑考虑
They said they'll think about it.

591
01:02:55,840 --> 01:02:57,360
很好
Good.

592
01:02:57,440 --> 01:03:00,200
可说实话 我觉得他们明天不会撤走的
To be honest, I don't think they'll leave tomorrow.

593
01:03:03,450 --> 01:03:06,660
我等不到明天了
I can't wait for tomorrow.

594
01:03:33,640 --> 01:03:36,320
法兰西正在流血
French blood is spilling.

595
01:03:39,620 --> 01:03:43,120
醒醒! 快点!
Wake up! Hurry!

596
01:03:45,160 --> 01:03:47,830
他们开战了 没有叫我
They've started the battle without me.

597
01:03:54,060 --> 01:03:57,360
马上去战斗 一定要胜利
There's a battle to fight and a war to be won.

598
01:04:01,440 --> 01:04:02,200
他妈的
Damn.

599
01:04:06,780 --> 01:04:08,210
撤退!
Sound the retreat!

600
