我的旗! 把旗给我!
My banner. My banner!

601
01:04:18,920 --> 01:04:20,220
打开大门!
Open the gate!

602
01:04:32,870 --> 01:04:36,240
怎么回事? 谁下令进攻的?
What happened? Who gave the order to attack?

603
01:04:36,310 --> 01:04:38,710
谁知道 这主意真是糟透了
God knows. It was a bad idea.

604
01:04:38,770 --> 01:04:40,670
士兵有没有做忏悔? 我们的牧师呢?
Were the men confessed? Where are the priests?

605
01:04:40,740 --> 01:04:43,870
没带牧师 我们想要发动突袭
We didn't take them. We wanted to make a surprise attack.

606
01:04:43,950 --> 01:04:46,280
迪努瓦 是你下令进攻的?
Dunois, was it you who gave the order to attack?

607
01:04:47,980 --> 01:04:50,510
 回答我!  我们能否以后再谈?
 Answer me!  Can we discuss this later?

608
01:04:50,590 --> 01:04:52,880
宜早不宜迟
Sooner is better than later.

609
01:04:52,960 --> 01:04:54,550
等等!
Wait!

610
01:04:56,830 --> 01:04:58,790
你会被砍死的!
You'll be killed!

611
