Let's plan this attack a little more carefully than this morning.

637
01:10:13,480 --> 01:10:15,070
说的对
Good idea.

638
01:10:19,520 --> 01:10:21,110
大人
Sire.

639
01:10:22,950 --> 01:10:25,850
有客人来访
We've got, uh, visitors.

640
01:10:45,740 --> 01:10:47,110
格拉斯代尔!
Glasdale!

641
01:10:48,940 --> 01:10:51,570
你听见了吗?
Do you hear me?

642
01:10:51,650 --> 01:10:53,910
你可以咒骂我...
You, who call me a whore...

643
01:10:53,980 --> 01:10:57,650
而我为你的灵魂感到悲哀...
I feel pity for you, for your soul...

644
01:10:57,720 --> 01:11:00,310
为你手下士兵的灵魂感到悲哀!
and for the souls of your men!

645
01:11:00,390 --> 01:11:04,490
投降吧! 向上帝投降吧!
Yield! Yield now to the King of Heaven!

646
01:11:05,560 --> 01:11:07,500
回到你们的岛国去!
Or go back to your island!

647
01:11:07,560 --> 01:11:11,120
你还是回到你的猪圈去吧!
And you, go back to your pigsty!

648
01:11:17,970 --> 01:11:19,570
在城墙布防
Man the walls.

649
01:11:40,960 --> 01:11:43,560
今天早上...
This morning...

650
01:11:43,630 --> 01:11:45,860
上帝赐予了我们一场胜利
God gave us a great victory.

651
01:11:48,940 --> 01:11:53,270
