在这你会死的! 快离开!
You're gonna get killed! Get out of here!

677
01:14:49,480 --> 01:14:51,010
来啊 打啊!
Come on, fight!

678
01:14:53,690 --> 01:14:55,180
发射! 打啊!
Go! Come on, fight!

679
01:15:01,900 --> 01:15:03,800
