快啊! 冲啊! 冲啊!
Hurry! Come on! Come on!

684
01:16:25,480 --> 01:16:26,880
好极了!
Yes!

685
01:16:26,950 --> 01:16:30,820
让你抢先把她杀了! 将军!
Hey, you just killed my woman! Captain!

686
01:16:33,090 --> 01:16:34,680
见鬼去吧
Go to hell.

687
