快叫医生来! 医生!
Call the physician! The physician!

688
01:16:41,430 --> 01:16:43,020
他妈的!
Damn it!

689
01:16:44,730 --> 01:16:46,100
路易斯 快叫医生来
Louis, find the physician.

690
01:16:47,640 --> 01:16:49,430
得把箭拔出来
We have to take out the arrow.

