And it's in deep.

704
01:17:38,490 --> 01:17:40,510
医生来之前你要挺住
You must stay still till the physician arrives.

705
01:17:40,590 --> 01:17:44,360
医生来了也是浪费时间 我们还是试试这个符咒吧
Physicians are a waste of time. We'll have more luck with this charm.

706
