It saved my life at Agincourt.

707
01:17:46,800 --> 01:17:49,560
我宁死也不靠这种魔咒
I'd rather die than use magic.

708
01:17:49,630 --> 01:17:52,160
如果再不拔出箭 你就死定了
You will die if that arrow stays in you much longer.

709
01:18:14,460 --> 01:18:19,590
这下好了 讨厌的东西没了
Well, at least this won't bother us anymore.

710
01:18:21,560 --> 01:18:25,160
我们去战场吧!
Now, let's go to the battle!

711
01:18:28,800 --> 01:18:30,570
拜托!
Please!

712
01:18:34,010 --> 01:18:36,100
她还真是够疯狂的
She's nuts.

713
01:18:36,180 --> 01:18:38,740
你冷静点 你必须休息
You must stay calm. You must rest.

714
01:18:38,810 --> 01:18:41,040
好 我休息
I'll rest.

715
01:18:41,120 --> 01:18:43,240
可你们都要...
But you have to...

716
01:18:43,320 --> 01:18:45,220
答应我
promise me...

717
01:18:45,290 --> 01:18:49,550
你们都返回战场上去
that you'll...that you'll go back to the battle.

718
01:18:49,620 --> 01:18:52,090
我答应你
I promise.

719
01:19:01,670 --> 01:19:03,640
快点!
Hurry!

720
01:19:03,710 --> 01:19:05,300
快! 救救她!
Quickly! Do something!

721
01:19:17,820 --> 01:19:18,980
她睡着了
She's sleeping.

722
01:19:19,050 --> 01:19:20,650
什么?
What?

723
01:19:31,470 --> 01:19:34,230
回来啊! 干吗跑啊?
Come on back! Why are you running away?

724
01:19:37,340 --> 01:19:39,270
 贞德还活着  很好
 Jeanne is alive.  Good.

725
01:19:39,340 --> 01:19:42,870
 我们要加强进攻  撤退
 We have to press on the attack.  Sound the retreat.

726
01:19:42,940 --> 01:19:45,470
 我答应了贞德要继续战斗的  我可没这么说
 I promised Jeanne we'd fight on.  I made no such promise.

727
01:19:45,550 --> 01:19:48,980
 晚上撤退  不 她不是这么下的命令
 Sound the retreat for the night.  No, that was her order.

728
01:19:49,050 --> 01:19:52,080
我已经受够她的命令了!
I'm fed up with taking her orders!

729
01:19:52,150 --> 01:19:54,920
她还说过会在天黑前打败英军!
She swore she'd defeat the English before nightfall!

730
01:19:54,990 --> 01:19:59,190
可她却去瞎逞英雄 还差点死了!
Instead, she goes and plays the fool, gets herself nearly killed!

731
01:19:59,260 --> 01:20:02,200
你看! 看看我们现在的处境!
Look! Look at the mess we're in!

732
01:20:02,260 --> 01:20:04,320
这都是她的错! 不是我的错!
That's her mess, not mine!

733
01:20:04,400 --> 01:20:07,460
如果没有她 我们的情况不会这么糟
We are worse off than if she'd never come at all.

734
01:20:07,540 --> 01:20:11,230
现在都听我的! 撤退!
Now do as I say and sound the retreat!

735
01:20:18,950 --> 01:20:21,850
你们去哪儿啊? 回来啊!
Where are you going? Hey, come back!

736
01:20:21,920 --> 01:20:24,320
回来接着打啊!
Come back and fight!

737
01:20:44,410 --> 01:20:47,380
 你在做什么?  给英国佬写信
 What are you making?  A message for the English.

738
01:20:52,650 --> 01:20:55,480
士兵们怎么说?
So, what are the men saying?

739
01:20:55,550 --> 01:20:58,280
她是上帝的恩赐
She's a gift from God.

740
01:20:58,350 --> 01:21:01,450
甚至有些人称她是圣人
Some even call her a saint.

741
01:21:01,520 --> 01:21:05,250
 就算去地狱 我也愿意陪着她  她叫你去 你真的去吗?
 I'd gladly follow her through hell.  Will you go that far if she asks you?

742
01:21:05,330 --> 01:21:08,560
当然会去 又不是没去过
Of course I will, and I've been there before.

743
01:21:13,600 --> 01:21:15,540
有件事情我闹不明白
There's one thing I don't quite understand.

744
01:21:15,600 --> 01:21:17,940
既然她是上帝派来的
She's been sent to us by God.

745
01:21:19,740 --> 01:21:21,680
上帝怎会能让她受这么重的伤呢?
Why does He allow her to be wounded so badly?

746
01:21:21,740 --> 01:21:26,180
那还不如问 她究竟是不是上帝派来的?
Maybe the good question is, is she really sent by God?

747
01:21:29,320 --> 01:21:31,480
这谁会知道?
Who knows?

748
01:21:31,550 --> 01:21:34,040
上帝知道
God knows.

749
01:22:32,850 --> 01:22:36,150
这女人还有把剑
Ooh. A woman with a sword.

750
01:22:43,220 --> 01:22:45,660
你弄坏了大爷的心情
You've hurt my feelings.

751
01:23:42,980 --> 01:23:44,820
法国佬们!
Frenchies!

752
01:23:44,890 --> 01:23:47,550
你们的宝贝天使怎么了?
What happened to your precious angel?

753
01:23:47,620 --> 01:23:51,650
啊? 法国佬们! 法国佬们!
Huh? Frenchies! Frenchies!

754
01:23:51,730 --> 01:23:54,820
我告诉你们吧!
I'll tell you what happened!

755
01:23:54,900 --> 01:23:58,560
我们把那个小娘们送回地狱去了...
We sent the little bitch back to hell...

756
01:23:58,630 --> 01:24:03,090
这样她就能找魔鬼寻欢了!
so she can go fuck with the devil!

757
01:24:05,310 --> 01:24:09,040
你们现在打算如何啊? 法国佬们
What are you gonna do now, Frenchies?

758
01:24:09,110 --> 01:24:12,880
出来打一仗如何啊? 来啊!
Why not come out and fight? Come on!

759
01:24:12,950 --> 01:24:17,180
来啊! 浑小子们! 醒醒吧!
Come on! Bastards, wake up!

760
01:24:17,250 --> 01:24:19,980
是不是正忙着祷告呢
Or are you too busy praying...

761
01:24:20,050 --> 01:24:24,420
以为那样做 那小娘们就能复活了?
to bring your little fucking witch back from the dead?

762
01:24:25,830 --> 01:24:27,760
听见了吗?
Do you hear me?

763
01:24:29,730 --> 01:24:31,790
我听见了!
I hear you!

764
01:24:36,140 --> 01:24:38,470
我还活着!
I'm alive!

765
01:24:42,380 --> 01:24:45,110
或许上帝能宽恕你的亵渎...
May God forgive your blasphemy...

766
01:24:48,220 --> 01:24:50,120
可我决不原谅
for I never will.

767
01:24:54,260 --> 01:24:55,850
决不原谅!
I never will!

768
01:25:05,800 --> 01:25:08,270
你在干什么? 你需要休息
What are you doing? You need to rest.

769
01:25:08,340 --> 01:25:10,930
必须把战士们都叫醒!
We must wake up the soldiers, now!

770
01:25:11,010 --> 01:25:13,530
好战士们 醒醒!
My fine soldiers, wake up!

771
01:25:15,880 --> 01:25:18,440
准备战斗! 准备战斗!
To arms! To arms!

772
01:25:18,510 --> 01:25:22,470
醒醒! 醒醒! 准备开战了!
Wake up! Wake up! We must fight the battle!

773
01:25:25,650 --> 01:25:29,490
战士们! 战斗就要开始了
My fine soldiers, the battle has begun!

774
01:25:34,660 --> 01:25:37,530
醒醒! 时机已经来到了!
Wake up! The time has come!

775
01:25:40,700 --> 01:25:43,600
战斗就要开始了!
The battle has begun!

776
01:25:43,670 --> 01:25:46,140
 准备战斗!  什么?
 To arms!  Yes?

777
01:25:46,210 --> 01:25:50,670
士兵们 把这座塔拉起来! 现在!
My soldiers, we need this tower up! We need this tower up, now!

778
01:25:56,720 --> 01:25:59,310
用力拉啊!
Pull!

779
01:26:03,730 --> 01:26:07,320
 这是干什么?  我们把塔还会去
 What's going on?  We're taking back the Tourelles.

780
01:26:15,870 --> 01:26:17,740
全体准备!
Get ready!

781
01:26:26,650 --> 01:26:29,210
去叫醒格拉斯代尔
Go wake up Glasdale.

782
01:26:45,500 --> 01:26:48,370
 你这是干什么?  给格拉斯代尔送个信儿
 What are you doing?  Sending a message to Glasdale.

783
01:26:49,470 --> 01:26:51,060
 就用它?  是的
 With that?  Yes.

784
01:26:51,140 --> 01:26:53,660
可你把它的背面冲向前面了
But you've got it back to front.

785
01:26:53,740 --> 01:26:55,680
听着 我知道自己在做什么
Listen, I know what I'm doing...

786
01:26:55,740 --> 01:27:00,240
要么过来帮把手 要么就回去睡你的觉去
so either lend a hand or get back to bed.

787
01:27:00,320 --> 01:27:03,580
我也要给格莱斯代尔送个信儿了
I'm going to send a message to Glasdale too.

788
01:27:08,620 --> 01:27:09,590
大人?
My lord?

789
01:27:11,130 --> 01:27:12,180
何事?
What?

790
01:27:13,830 --> 01:27:17,420
那个法国女人又活过来了
The French witch, she's back from the dead.

791
01:27:17,500 --> 01:27:19,430
快点 士兵们!
Hurry up, men!

792
01:27:20,700 --> 01:27:24,230
我们还是再仔细考虑考虑吧
Don't you think we should take some time to think about this?

793
01:27:24,310 --> 01:27:26,240
宜早不宜迟
Sooner is better than later.

794
01:27:32,750 --> 01:27:35,770
准备战斗! 准备战斗!
To arms! To arms!

795
01:27:35,850 --> 01:27:37,440
早上好
Good morning.

796
01:27:43,190 --> 01:27:44,780
用这个
This one.

797
01:27:48,360 --> 01:27:50,330
她到底耍的什么把戏?
What the fuck is she playing at?

798
01:27:50,400 --> 01:27:54,100
我不知道! 问题是她现在在干啥?
I don't know! The question is, what is she doing now?

799
01:27:54,170 --> 01:27:57,230
她什么都不跟我们商量 我们怎么做事?
How can we plan anything if she doesn't consult with us?

800
01:27:57,310 --> 01:27:59,800
 我们昨天跟她商量了吗?  少提这茬
 Did we consult with her yesterday?  Don't even start.

801
01:27:59,870 --> 01:28:02,570
 你昨天也是同意进攻的  是啊 可那不算
 You agreed to attack yesterday too.  Yes, but that doesn't count.

802
01:28:02,640 --> 01:28:05,510
 为啥?  因为我一辈子都同意进攻
 Why is that?  Because I always agree to attack.

803
01:28:05,580 --> 01:28:06,740
准备战斗!
To arms!

804
01:28:14,390 --> 01:28:16,620
疯婆子
Crazy bitch.

805
01:28:16,690 --> 01:28:18,630
她连怎么用都不知道
She doesn't even know how to use it.

806
01:28:31,440 --> 01:28:32,700
天哪!
Oh, my God!

807
01:28:41,420 --> 01:28:44,650
 靠! 快关城门!  关城门!
 Fuck! Close the doors!  Close the doors!

808
01:28:56,200 --> 01:28:59,330
 开门啊!  给"箭猪"装箭!
 Open the door!  Load the porcupine!

809
01:29:08,080 --> 01:29:09,510
用力拉!
Pull!

810
01:29:25,060 --> 01:29:26,750
拉!
And pull!

811
01:29:29,930 --> 01:29:32,060
快! 动作快点!
Come on! Hurry up!

812
01:29:45,010 --> 01:29:46,380
来吧!
Come on!

813
01:30:01,000 --> 01:30:04,060
不要企盼奇迹 待在这儿
Never wait for miracles. Stay there.

814
01:30:08,640 --> 01:30:11,400
法国娘们! 来抓我啊!
French whore! Come and get me!

815
01:30:13,980 --> 01:30:15,700
还等什么呢?
What are you waiting for?

816
01:30:18,550 --> 01:30:21,450
什么事? 贞德!
Yes? Oh,Jeanne!

817
01:30:22,720 --> 01:30:25,410
准备火箭手! 烧城门!
Find your archers and burn that door!

818
01:30:25,490 --> 01:30:26,980
马上办!
Right away!

819
01:30:31,460 --> 01:30:32,620
推!
Push!

820
01:30:40,870 --> 01:30:43,930
城门准备!
Prepare the gate! Come on!

821
01:30:44,010 --> 01:30:46,100
弓箭手就位!
Position!

822
01:30:48,710 --> 01:30:50,300
放!
Fire!

823
01:30:56,450 --> 01:30:57,680
拿水来!
Water!

824
01:30:57,750 --> 01:30:59,240
放!
Fire!

825
01:31:06,260 --> 01:31:07,850
上帝啊!
Oh, my God!

826
01:31:14,770 --> 01:31:16,360
杀了她
Kill her.

827
01:31:18,810 --> 01:31:21,600
他妈的 装箭!
Fuck. Reload!

828
01:31:21,680 --> 01:31:22,700
再来些弓箭手!
More archers!

829
01:31:50,300 --> 01:31:52,030
漂亮
Perfect.

830
01:31:55,140 --> 01:31:56,700
再来些弓箭手!
More archers!

831
01:31:56,780 --> 01:31:58,070
帮帮我!
Help me!

832
01:32:09,490 --> 01:32:12,390
集合你的人! 准备攻城车!
Get your men! We'll load this up as a battering ram!

833
01:32:12,460 --> 01:32:14,330
早做好了
Already done.

834
01:32:47,330 --> 01:32:49,350
 怎么了?  没事
 What?  Nothing.

835
01:32:54,100 --> 01:32:57,090
那帮我抬这些人
Help me with these men, please.

836
01:32:57,170 --> 01:32:58,760
是的
Yes.

837
01:33:00,610 --> 01:33:02,200
遵命
As you command.

838
01:33:14,320 --> 01:33:16,260
等等 你要干什么?
Wait. What are you doing?

839
01:33:16,320 --> 01:33:20,090
撞开城门 你不是这么想的吗?
We're going to open that door. Isn't that what you want?

840
01:33:23,200 --> 01:33:25,130
快给我让开!
Get out of my fucking way!

841
01:33:30,370 --> 01:33:31,960
把锅加满!
Fill the cauldron!

842
01:33:34,880 --> 01:33:37,280
该死的法国人! 看我怎么收拾你们
Fucking French! What the fuck do you know about me?

843
01:33:44,390 --> 01:33:45,910
装箭 装箭!
Reload. Reload!

844
01:33:52,490 --> 01:33:55,930
快把锅倒满! 你们等什么呢?
Fill the fucking cauldron! What are you waiting for?

845
01:34:00,370 --> 01:34:02,800
来人! 来人!
More men! More men!

846
01:34:15,120 --> 01:34:16,710
预备!
Ready!

847
01:34:41,410 --> 01:34:44,310
倒油! 倒油!
Pour the oil! Pour the oil!

848
01:35:38,430 --> 01:35:41,490
你在干什么? 贞德
What are you doing,Jeanne?

849
01:35:43,500 --> 01:35:44,800
我在玩
I'm playing.

850
01:36:03,200 --> 01:36:07,200
你对我做了些什么? 贞德
What are you doing to me,Jeanne?

851
01:36:24,360 --> 01:36:26,050
听见我说了吗?
Do you hear me?

852
01:36:26,120 --> 01:36:28,460
你怎么了?
Are you all right?

853
01:36:28,530 --> 01:36:31,090
能听见我说话吗? 冷静一下
Do you hear me? Calm down.

854
01:36:31,160 --> 01:36:33,430
结束了
It's over.

855
01:36:33,500 --> 01:36:35,060
我们赢了
We won.

856
01:36:35,130 --> 01:36:37,100
 赢了?  是的
 We won?  Yes.

857
01:36:44,540 --> 01:36:46,910
臭婆娘
Fucking bitch.

858
01:36:50,050 --> 01:36:53,480
我的朋友! 我的战友! 快过来
My friend! My soldier! In my arms.

859
01:36:56,290 --> 01:36:58,650
 我们赢了?  赢?
 We won?  Won?

860
01:36:58,720 --> 01:37:02,250
错了 贞德 怎么能用这个小词呢
No. No,Jeanne. So small a word will never do.

861
01:37:02,330 --> 01:37:05,630
这是胜利!
This is victory!

862
01:37:05,700 --> 01:37:08,490
这是荣誉!
This is glory!

863
01:37:35,390 --> 01:37:37,260
你怎么了?
What's the matter?

864
01:37:41,270 --> 01:37:43,200
这就是荣誉?
This is glory?

865
01:37:47,000 --> 01:37:48,940
不要紧的
Doesn't matter.

866
01:37:55,810 --> 01:37:57,870
这不可能
This is not possible.

867
01:38:12,060 --> 01:38:13,550
这不可能
It is not possible.

868
01:38:13,630 --> 01:38:17,400
你看起来很失望啊 这不是你想要的?
You look disappointed. Isn't this what you wanted?

869
01:38:17,470 --> 01:38:21,130
不 不该是这样的
No. Not like this.

870
01:38:21,210 --> 01:38:24,140
几周来你一直渴望着这一切
For weeks you've been asking for this.

871
01:38:24,210 --> 01:38:27,140
现在你得到了
Well, now you have it.

872
01:38:35,490 --> 01:38:37,180
 你要干什么?  没什么
 What are you doing?  Nothing.

873
01:38:37,250 --> 01:38:39,450
我只是想要他的牙
I'm just taking his teeth.

874
01:38:41,430 --> 01:38:44,360
你不能为了想要一个人的牙就杀了他
But you just can't kill a man for his teeth.

875
01:38:44,430 --> 01:38:46,420
为什么不? 他的牙很不赖
Why not? He has good teeth.

876
01:38:47,900 --> 01:38:50,660
你...你不能这么做!
Because...Because you can't!

877
01:38:52,400 --> 01:38:54,060
那这一切又是什么?
What about all this?

878
01:38:54,140 --> 01:38:56,770
那不一样
But that's different.

879
01:38:56,840 --> 01:39:00,540
我们战斗是为了我们的理想
I mean, we were fighting for a cause.

880
01:39:00,610 --> 01:39:03,980
我不是 他是我的俘虏
Not me. He's my prisoner...

881
01:39:04,050 --> 01:39:05,740
要不要他的牙是我的事
I can take his teeth if I want to.

882
01:39:05,820 --> 01:39:09,380
你不能这样! 住手!
No, you can't! Stop it!

883
01:39:09,450 --> 01:39:10,890
给 拿着!
Here. Take this!

884
01:39:12,020 --> 01:39:14,990
现在他是我的了 而你
He's mine now. Here, you.

885
01:39:15,060 --> 01:39:17,190
走吧
Go.

886
01:39:19,400 --> 01:39:22,020
做的好啊 那其他战俘怎么办?
Bravo. And what about all the other prisoners?

887
01:39:22,100 --> 01:39:25,070
 全放他们走?  我不知道
 Do we let them go too?  I don't know.

888
01:39:27,440 --> 01:39:28,530
也许吧
Maybe.

889
01:39:36,510 --> 01:39:40,450
我们必须去忏悔 我们必须去忏悔
We must confess. We must confess.

890
01:39:42,450 --> 01:39:45,350
我们要做忏悔 所有人都做
Please, we have to be confessed. All of us.

891
01:39:50,490 --> 01:39:53,520
我知道这不符合一般习惯...
I know this is not normal custom...

892
01:39:53,600 --> 01:39:55,430
可是
but, uh...

893
01:39:59,470 --> 01:40:02,700
一切会好起来的 他会听我们忏悔的
Everything's gonna be fine. He's gonna confess us.

894
01:40:05,610 --> 01:40:07,910
跪下 都跪下
Kneel. Kneel.

895
01:40:19,120 --> 01:40:21,350
阿朗松带来个坏消息
Alencon brings bad news.

896
01:40:21,430 --> 01:40:25,490
上千名英军正在河岸远处集结
Thousands of English are forming up on the far side of the river.

897
01:40:25,560 --> 01:40:28,000
我们要清点一下人数 准备作战了
I think we should count our men and get ready.

898
01:40:29,170 --> 01:40:30,290
我们走
Let's go.

899
01:41:10,240 --> 01:41:11,830
我过去
I'll go.

900
01:41:14,780 --> 01:41:17,010
一个人过去
Alone.

901
01:41:45,680 --> 01:41:48,080
告诉你们的国王 亨利!
I have a message for your King Henry!

902
01:41:49,250 --> 01:41:51,840
这是上帝给他的音讯!
It is a message from God!

903
01:41:52,750 --> 01:41:54,340
回家吧!
Go home!

904
01:41:57,220 --> 01:42:00,050
静静地回去吧!
Go now, in peace!

905
01:42:00,960 --> 01:42:04,760
你们不走的话 这里就将是你们的葬身之地!
If you do not go now, you will be buried in this field!

906
01:42:07,200 --> 01:42:12,600
我已经看够了鲜血!
I've seen enough blood!

907
01:42:13,900 --> 01:42:15,840
可如果你们还想看...
But if you want more...

908
01:42:17,370 --> 01:42:19,000
那我也无法阻拦你们!
I can't stop you!

909
01:42:20,680 --> 01:42:24,580
我要说的是 看到的只会是你们的鲜血...
I can only warn you that it will be your blood...

910
01:42:25,950 --> 01:42:27,140
不会是我们的!
not ours!

911
01:42:28,950 --> 01:42:32,550
我等你们的答复
I'm waiting for your answer.

912
01:42:47,870 --> 01:42:51,570
不要期待奇迹 准备战斗
Never wait for miracles. Stand by to attack.

913
01:43:04,450 --> 01:43:06,290
求你了
Please.

914
01:43:13,400 --> 01:43:15,130
主啊...
My Lord...

915
01:43:16,530 --> 01:43:17,830
求你了
please.

916
01:43:49,600 --> 01:43:52,470
那就是他妈所谓的奇迹了
Now that's what I call a goddamn bloody miracle.

917
01:43:52,540 --> 01:43:54,730
她跨着白色战马 孤身前往...
She was on her white horse alone...

918
01:43:54,810 --> 01:43:57,240
面对全部英军 逼退了他们...
facing the whole English army, and she drove them away...

919
01:43:57,310 --> 01:44:00,240
现在奥尔良自由了
and now Orleans is free.

920
01:44:10,790 --> 01:44:12,310
我们失去了奥尔良
We lost Orleans.

921
01:44:13,760 --> 01:44:15,550
我要抓住那个女孩
I want that girl.

922
01:44:18,500 --> 01:44:22,060
我要烧死她
I want that girl burned.

923
01:44:42,150 --> 01:44:45,380
我能见见裁缝吗? 太紧了 我喘不过气了
May I see the seamstress? It's too tight. I can't breathe.

924
01:44:45,460 --> 01:44:48,980
那也算是皇冠? 没有更好点的吗?
That's meant to be a crown? Don't you have something more regal?

925
01:44:49,060 --> 01:44:51,080
英国人把真的拿走了
The English took the real one.

926
01:44:51,160 --> 01:44:54,720
浑身脏的时间太长了 我都忘了干净是什么样了
It's been muddy so long I forgot how good it looked cleaned up.

927
01:44:54,800 --> 01:44:57,730
你里面也弄干净了吗?
But did you remember to clean up what's inside as well?

928
01:44:57,800 --> 01:45:00,930
我要的是个宏大的加冕礼 你这算什么?
I ask for a grandiose coronation, and this is what you give?

929
01:45:01,000 --> 01:45:03,770
真是彻底的失败啊!
This whole thing is going to be an utter fiasco!

930
01:45:03,840 --> 01:45:07,470
你只给我三天时间准备 你父亲的加冕准备了三个月
You gave me 3 days to prepare. Your father's coronation took 3 months.

931
01:45:07,540 --> 01:45:09,310
说的对 看来我们应该推迟了
He's right. We should call for a delay.

932
01:45:09,380 --> 01:45:11,750
没时间了 我们不能停下来
No time. We can't hold up the ceremony.

933
01:45:11,820 --> 01:45:13,210
谁知道英国人什么时候还会回来
No telling when the English might come back.

934
01:45:13,280 --> 01:45:16,580
回来好啊 让他们瞧瞧法国真正的国王
Let them come. Let them see who is the true king of France.

935
01:45:26,300 --> 01:45:29,930
该死的英国人 我们本该在巴黎圣母院举行仪式的
Those damn English. We should be doing this in Paris in Notre Dame.

936
01:45:30,000 --> 01:45:32,160
那会比这个隆重两倍
It is much more prestigious and twice as big.

937
01:45:32,240 --> 01:45:35,430
大小不重要 神圣才是关键 对吧主教?
It is the sacred place that matters, not the size. Correct, Bishop?

938
01:45:35,510 --> 01:45:39,410
是的夫人 法国的国王必须...
Yes, my lady. True kings of France must be anointed...

939
01:45:39,480 --> 01:45:42,210
在伟大的兰斯大教堂施以涂油礼
in our great cathedral of Reims with the holy oil of Clovis.

940
01:45:53,760 --> 01:45:56,490
阁下! 好像没有油了
Your Grace! There can be no anointing.

941
01:45:56,560 --> 01:46:00,660
 你说什么呢?  施礼用的油不见了
 What are you talking about?  The holy oil of Clovis is all gone.

942
01:46:00,730 --> 01:46:02,130
不见了? 不可能
Gone? That's impossible.

943
01:46:02,200 --> 01:46:06,000
那可是神油 是不会用尽的
It's a magic oil. A miraculous oil. It can never be exhausted.

944
01:46:06,070 --> 01:46:08,200
 您自己看看  有问题吗?
 Look for yourself.  Problem?

945
01:46:08,270 --> 01:46:10,260
这就奇怪了
I just don't understand.

946
01:46:10,340 --> 01:46:13,430
上次我看的时候 油还满满的
The oil of Clovis. It was quite full the last time I saw it.

947
01:46:13,510 --> 01:46:17,040
 上次是什么时候?  查尔斯六世加冕的时候
 And when was that?  At the coronation of King Charles VI.

948
01:46:17,110 --> 01:46:20,080
三十年前? 那它消失有什么奇怪的?
Thirty years ago? Does it surprise you it's gone?

949
01:46:20,150 --> 01:46:23,050
你不明白
But you don't understand.

950
01:46:23,120 --> 01:46:27,250
那是神油 非比寻常
It's no ordinary oil. It's a miraculous oil.

951
01:46:27,320 --> 01:46:30,890
是天堂来的白鸽子送来这里...
It was brought by a white dove from heaven...

952
01:46:30,960 --> 01:46:33,830
给国王加冕用的
to crown King Clovis in this very cathedral.

953
01:46:34,900 --> 01:46:38,160
 你干什么?  完成这个奇迹
 What are you doing?  Performing a miracle.

954
01:47:57,980 --> 01:48:02,350
神油在此 万能的主保佑...
With this sacred oil, blessed by the hand of God the Father Almighty...

955
01:48:02,420 --> 01:48:05,250
向你施以涂油礼 查尔斯·瓦罗亚...
we do anoint thee, Charles Valois...

956
01:48:05,320 --> 01:48:10,350
成为法兰西至高无上的国王...
to be sovereign lord and king of this great kingdom of France...

957
01:48:10,430 --> 01:48:14,800
在你的有生之年...
charging that ye should defend the faith of our Mother Holy Church...

958
01:48:14,870 --> 01:48:17,560
维护教会的信仰
as long as ye shall live.

959
01:48:18,640 --> 01:48:19,900
阿门
Amen.

960
01:48:54,670 --> 01:48:56,610
国王万岁!
Long live the king!

961
01:49:14,520 --> 01:49:17,890
 贞德 你没事吧?  是 我没事
 Jeanne, are you all right?  Yes, I'm fine.

962
01:49:20,560 --> 01:49:24,090
 你盯着我干什么?  你腿上中箭了
 Why are you staring at me?  You have an arrow in your leg.

963
01:49:29,840 --> 01:49:31,700
知道了
So there is.

964
01:49:33,140 --> 01:49:35,200
可那不耽误你接着攀墙啊!
But that doesn't stop you from climbing!

965
01:49:36,380 --> 01:49:39,970
快去攀! 快去!
Well, climb! Go! Go!

966
01:49:45,620 --> 01:49:47,180
把这支箭拔出来
Take this arrow out.

967
01:49:52,530 --> 01:49:54,330
留神!
Look out!

968
01:49:55,700 --> 01:49:59,100
 小心点!  贞德 士兵已经疲惫不堪了
 Be careful!  Jeanne, the men are exhausted.

969
01:49:59,170 --> 01:50:01,970
我知道 可敌人正在撤退 巴黎就要是我们的了
I know, but so is the enemy. They're falling back. Paris is ours.

970
01:50:02,040 --> 01:50:04,100
贞德 我们人不够了
Jeanne, we are not enough.

971
01:50:04,170 --> 01:50:06,870
那就把援军调过来
So bring up the reinforcements.

972
01:50:06,940 --> 01:50:08,910
援军? 哪儿有?
Reinforcements? Where?

973
01:50:10,110 --> 01:50:12,080
就在我们后面
Right behind us.

974
01:50:12,150 --> 01:50:14,880
迪努瓦带着他的一万人马
Dunois with another 1 0,000 men.

975
01:50:14,950 --> 01:50:18,150
 贞德 你自己回头看看  只看前方 不要回头
 Jeanne, look behind you.  Never look behind. Only ahead.

976
01:50:20,220 --> 01:50:23,090
你知道怎么数数吗?
Do you know how to count?

977
01:50:25,600 --> 01:50:29,430
我当然会! 把他们调过来!
Of course I do! So, bring them up!

978
01:50:32,000 --> 01:50:36,230
贞德 那可不是一万援军!
Jeanne, that is not 1 0,000 reinforcements!

979
01:50:36,310 --> 01:50:38,370
那只是一百名...
That is 100...

980
01:50:38,440 --> 01:50:41,210
忠心无比但又疲惫不堪的士兵!
very loyal but very tired soldiers!

981
01:50:43,010 --> 01:50:45,540
迪努瓦呢?
But where's Dunois?

982
01:50:45,620 --> 01:50:47,710
国王答应给我的军队呢?
And where are the men the king promised me?

983
01:50:47,780 --> 01:50:51,310
他跟本就没派军队! 你还不明白吗?
He never sent them! Don't you understand?

984
01:50:51,390 --> 01:50:53,550
他不想再打仗了
He doesn't want this war anymore.

985
01:50:53,620 --> 01:50:56,590
他已经得到王冠了 他已经满足了
He has his crown now. That's all he ever wanted.

986
01:50:57,830 --> 01:51:00,890
可是那些声音 他们明明答应我的
But my voices, they promised me.

987
01:51:00,960 --> 01:51:03,690
去你的奇怪声音吧!
To hell with your voices!

988
01:51:06,840 --> 01:51:09,240
面对现实吧!
It's time to face facts!

989
01:51:11,570 --> 01:51:14,410
我们不该来这儿!
We have nothing to do here!

990
01:51:14,480 --> 01:51:16,410
谁都不该来!
None of us!

991
01:51:18,650 --> 01:51:20,580
甚至是你
Not even you.

992
01:51:25,620 --> 01:51:28,090
你们不再相信我了吗?
You don't believe in me anymore?

993
01:51:28,160 --> 01:51:31,180
贞德 我们当然还相信你
Jeanne, of course we still believe in you.

994
01:51:31,260 --> 01:51:35,460
如果我说了算 我要把英国人全赶到海里去
If it were up to me, I'd chase every goddamn Englishman into the ocean.

995
01:51:35,530 --> 01:51:38,190
可我们说了不算
But it's not up to us anymore.

996
01:51:38,270 --> 01:51:40,200
国王说了才算
It's up to the king.

997
01:51:52,320 --> 01:51:54,310
我们回去吧 贞德
You should go home,Jeanne.

998
01:52:08,870 --> 01:52:12,800
她要的军队太庞大 我们无法负担
We cannot possibly afford to pay for the size of army she's demanding.

999
01:52:12,870 --> 01:52:14,200
那女孩疯了
Girl is crazy.

1000
01:52:16,410 --> 01:52:18,600
她在奥尔良的胜利是个奇迹
Her victory at Orleans was a miracle.

1001
01:52:18,680 --> 01:52:22,170
可我们建造法国的未来是不能靠奇迹的
But we can't wait for a miracle when we build a future for France.

1002
01:52:24,710 --> 01:52:27,480
巴黎一战是场灾难
Paris was a disaster.

1003
01:52:27,550 --> 01:52:29,540
上帝已经不跟她在一起了
God wasn't with her then.

1004
01:52:29,620 --> 01:52:32,680
如果上帝抛弃了她 我们该怎么办?
If God deserts her, what do you think we should do?

1005
01:52:44,570 --> 01:52:48,500
你为什么出卖我? 再给我几百人巴黎就是我们的了
Why did you betray me? Paris was ours. All I needed was a few hundred men.

1006
01:52:48,570 --> 01:52:53,100
 为什么你不派给我军队?  给你?
 Why did you take the army you gave me?  Gave you?

1007
01:52:53,180 --> 01:52:56,580
 我当时的意思可不是这个  那你什么意思?
 I wouldn't quite put it that way.  So how would you put it?

1008
01:53:01,820 --> 01:53:05,080
我们 很感激...
We are, of course, enormously grateful...

1009
01:53:05,160 --> 01:53:07,560
你过去所做的贡献
for your past efforts...

1010
01:53:07,620 --> 01:53:10,180
现在你的任务已经完成了
but now your task is done.

1011
01:53:10,260 --> 01:53:12,660
是该进行和谈的时候了
Now is the time for negotiation.

1012
01:53:12,730 --> 01:53:14,960
只有战争才能从英国人那里得到和平
Peace will only be got with the English by the end of a lance.

1013
01:53:15,030 --> 01:53:19,300
你就这么嗜血如命? 你很享受吗?
Why are you so bloodthirsty? Do you enjoy it?

1014
01:53:21,870 --> 01:53:24,640
外交手段要更文明...
Diplomacy is far more civilized...

1015
01:53:24,710 --> 01:53:27,730
更安全 也更廉价
far safer and far cheaper.

1016
01:53:35,550 --> 01:53:40,180
这是受围困的城来的信 那里的百姓都要饿死了...
I've letters here from towns under siege, where your people are starving...

1017
01:53:40,260 --> 01:53:42,950
祈求上帝去帮帮他们
begging God on their knees to help them.

1018
01:53:43,030 --> 01:53:46,890
我要去给他们答复 你去要阻拦我?
I'm here to answer their prayers. And you want to stop me?

1019
01:53:49,130 --> 01:53:52,570
法国不是属于你个人的 查尔斯
France does not belong to you, Charles.

1020
01:53:52,640 --> 01:53:54,930
她是属于上帝的
She belongs to God.

1021
01:54:05,880 --> 01:54:08,780
她能乖乖回家就好了
If only she would just go home.

1022
01:54:28,400 --> 01:54:30,030
那我现在怎么办?
So what am I supposed to do now?

1023
01:54:31,370 --> 01:54:34,740
 你们有得到什么启示吗?  已经好几周听不见他们的声音了
 What do your voices say?  They haven't spoken to me in weeks.

1024
01:54:34,810 --> 01:54:37,010
是从加冕礼以后
Not since the coronation.

1025
01:54:37,080 --> 01:54:39,070
没有任何征兆
No signs, nothing.

1026
01:54:40,620 --> 01:54:42,780
或许他们的沉默就是一种指示
Maybe their silence is a sign.

1027
01:54:43,850 --> 01:54:46,520
 就是让你回家去  不是的
 Maybe it's a sign to go home.  No.

1028
01:54:46,590 --> 01:54:49,580
还不是时候 我的使命还没有完成
It's not time yet. My mission isn't over yet.

1029
01:54:50,990 --> 01:54:54,900
 我还有好多要做的事  可你怎么做...
 There's still more I have to do.  But how do...

1030
01:54:54,960 --> 01:54:56,960
你怎么知道...
How do you know that these...

1031
01:54:57,030 --> 01:55:00,090
那些声音就是对你说的?
these voices aren't just really you?

1032
01:55:01,540 --> 01:55:05,910
是对我说的 上帝就是这样指示我的
Well, they are me. That's how God speaks to me.

1033
01:55:07,680 --> 01:55:11,240
如果你仔仔细细的听 你也能听见的
Even you could hear them if you listened hard enough.

1034
01:55:12,920 --> 01:55:15,010
你说的太容易了
You make it sound so simple.

1035
01:55:16,690 --> 01:55:18,980
连你也不再相信我了
So even you don't believe in me anymore.

1036
01:55:19,060 --> 01:55:23,890
贞德 我比任何人都信任你
Jeanne, I believe in you more than anyone.

1037
01:55:23,960 --> 01:55:27,160
我只是希望...
I just wish I could...

1038
01:55:27,230 --> 01:55:29,820
我能帮帮你
help you.

1039
01:55:29,900 --> 01:55:32,800
想帮我 做一件事就可以了
There is one thing you can do if you want to help me.

1040
01:55:32,870 --> 01:55:34,000
告诉我
Tell me.

1041
01:55:34,070 --> 01:55:36,800
让国王把他许诺的军队给我
Tell the king to give back the army that he gave me.

1042
01:55:47,250 --> 01:55:49,680
我们必须阻止她 陛下
We have to stop her, Your Majesty.

1043
01:55:49,750 --> 01:55:53,020
如果她率领军队 攻打勃艮第...
If she raises an army and attacks the Burgundians...

1044
01:55:53,090 --> 01:55:56,060
那几个月的和谈就白费了
months of negotiations will have been in vain.

1045
01:55:57,490 --> 01:55:59,720
贞德为我们已经做的够多的了
Jeanne has done so much for us.

1046
01:55:59,800 --> 01:56:03,290
我自己也是十分敬佩她
I can assure you, the maid has no greater admirer than myself.

1047
01:56:03,370 --> 01:56:06,300
可不论我们个人怎么想 我们也不能...
Whatever our personal feelings, we cannot allow her to conduct...

1048
01:56:06,370 --> 01:56:09,000
让她为了报仇去打仗
her own private war.

1049
01:56:09,070 --> 01:56:13,070
为了国家着想您不能让她去康比涅
For the sake of the kingdom, you must stop her from going to Compiegne.

1050
01:56:13,140 --> 01:56:15,700
我阻止不了她
I can't stop her.

1051
01:56:15,780 --> 01:56:20,880
如果你不原意的话 勃艮第人会原意帮您的
Well, if you don't, I'm sure the Burgundians would be happy to oblige.

1052
01:56:20,950 --> 01:56:23,420
或许他们可以在康比涅抓住她...
If they capture her at Compiegne...

1053
01:56:23,490 --> 01:56:25,750
那就没人会怪罪我们了
No one could blame us.

1054
01:56:27,590 --> 01:56:32,430
可那好像是我们出卖了她
But it could sound like we betrayed her.

1055
01:56:32,500 --> 01:56:34,960
 不 没有  上帝啊 不是
 No, never.  Good heavens, no.

1056
01:56:35,030 --> 01:56:37,230
别担心 查尔斯
Don't worry, Charles.

1057
01:56:39,600 --> 01:56:43,970
如果上帝仍然与她同在 她会胜利的
If God is still with her, she will be victorious.

1058
01:56:44,040 --> 01:56:46,270
可她的军队是那么少
But her army's so much smaller.

1059
01:56:46,340 --> 01:56:49,440
那她的信仰可要更强烈才行
Then her faith will have to be bigger.

1060
01:57:03,830 --> 01:57:07,690
 你干什么? 快开门  我不能拿自己的城冒险
 What are you doing? Open this gate.  I can't risk the safety of my town.

1061
01:57:10,230 --> 01:57:11,830
拿着我的旗!
Take my banner!

1062
01:58:09,460 --> 01:58:10,860
上帝啊
My Lord.

1063
01:58:12,260 --> 01:58:14,090
上帝啊
My Lord.

1064
01:58:39,190 --> 01:58:40,950
真不敢相信
I can't believe it.

1065
01:58:41,020 --> 01:58:45,890
你幻想中的死亡竟是遍地长满了草
Your romantic vision of death with all that grass growing everywhere.

1066
01:58:45,960 --> 01:58:48,620
我必须承认你的想象力是很强
I must admit, you have a big imagination.

1067
01:58:48,700 --> 01:58:51,430
可还是不够
But maybe not big enough.

1068
01:58:51,500 --> 01:58:55,770
死亡其实很简单
Death is much more simple.

1069
01:58:58,980 --> 01:59:02,600
几个月后会变得更有趣些
After a few months, it gets more interesting.

1070
01:59:05,310 --> 01:59:09,080
一年后就会变得...
Then after a year, it finally becomes...

1071
01:59:11,320 --> 01:59:13,150
虚无缥缈
romantic.

1072
01:59:18,030 --> 01:59:19,590
你是谁?
Who are you?

1073
01:59:19,660 --> 01:59:22,500
不喜欢我这张脸?
You don't like my face?

1074
01:59:22,570 --> 01:59:24,900
这张你或许会喜欢
Maybe you'd prefer this one.

1075
01:59:28,370 --> 01:59:30,360
可能太小了
Too young, maybe.

1076
01:59:30,440 --> 01:59:33,100
这一张呢?
How about this one?

1077
01:59:34,780 --> 01:59:39,610
好些了吗? 还没完呢
Better now? But incomplete.

1078
01:59:44,890 --> 01:59:48,190
我识破你了 撒旦
Get thee behind me, Satan.

1079
01:59:48,260 --> 01:59:52,960
你以为你是谁 竟能区分出善恶?
Who are you to even think you can know the difference between good and evil?

1080
01:59:55,060 --> 01:59:56,460
你是上帝吗?
Are you God?

1081
02:00:00,800 --> 02:00:03,400
我只是一个信使
I'm just a messenger.

1082
02:00:03,470 --> 02:00:04,870
他需要我
He needs me.

1083
02:00:04,940 --> 02:00:09,040
你竟然会认为万能的上帝...
How can you imagine that God, the creator of heaven and Earth...

1084
02:00:09,110 --> 02:00:11,170
创造万物的神灵...
the source of all life...

1085
02:00:11,250 --> 02:00:15,450
可能会需要你?
could possibly need you?

1086
02:00:16,690 --> 02:00:17,780
我不知道
I don't know.

1087
02:00:17,850 --> 02:00:20,820
他无能到连自己的音讯都没法送?
You don't think He's big enough to deliver His own messages?

1088
02:00:21,690 --> 02:00:24,290
你要对我做什么?
What do you want from me?

1089
02:00:24,360 --> 02:00:26,690
没什么 我是来放你走的
Nothing. I'm here to set you free.

1090
02:00:29,200 --> 02:00:31,630
笑一下 有人来了
I said smile. You have visitors.

1091
02:00:31,700 --> 02:00:33,690
勃艮第的公爵
The Duke of Burgundy.

1092
02:00:45,480 --> 02:00:48,080
这位就是声名显赫的贞德吧...
So here's the famous Jeanne...

1093
02:00:48,150 --> 02:00:51,680
奥尔良的救世主 英国人的噩梦
savior of Orleans, terror of the English.

1094
02:00:51,750 --> 02:00:55,380
你要多少赎金 我的国王都会给的
My king will pay any ransom you ask.

1095
02:00:55,460 --> 02:00:58,950
你的国王? 是啊 当然
Your king? Oh, yes, of course.

1096
02:00:59,030 --> 02:01:01,790
可他付给我什么呢? 是牛? 还是鸡?
What's he gonna pay me with? Cows? Chickens?

1097
02:01:01,860 --> 02:01:05,320
我还是喜欢金子 英国人给了我不少
I prefer gold, and the English have plenty.

1098
02:01:06,700 --> 02:01:10,540
不知道为了抓住奥尔良的巫婆 他们会付多少钱呢
I wonder how much they'll pay to have the witch of Orleans in their clutches.

1099
02:01:10,610 --> 02:01:15,270
英国人一向傲慢 无法接受被一个村姑击败的事实
The English are so arrogant, they can't accept being defeated by a peasant girl.

1100
02:01:15,340 --> 02:01:17,870
那肯定是魔鬼干的
It has to have been the devil's work.

1101
02:01:17,950 --> 02:01:20,440
是上帝打败了英军
God defeated the English.

1102
02:01:20,520 --> 02:01:22,980
那也是上帝让你被俘的?
And God allowed you to be caught?

1103
02:01:24,590 --> 02:01:26,320
从个人来说 我不信上帝
Personally, I don't believe in God.

1104
02:01:26,390 --> 02:01:28,860
我也不信魔鬼
I don't believe in the devil either.

1105
02:01:28,920 --> 02:01:31,860
所以我从来不会失望
That's why I'm never disappointed.

1106
02:01:33,860 --> 02:01:35,520
卖了她
Sell her.

1107
02:01:52,580 --> 02:01:54,240
为了付贞德的赎金
To payJeanne's ransom.

1108
02:01:54,320 --> 02:01:57,550
这是将军们凑的钱 还有奥尔良的百姓
The captains gave what they could, as well as citizens of Orleans.

1109
02:01:57,620 --> 02:02:02,350
你们太慷慨了 有多少?
That's very generous of you. How much?

1110
02:02:02,430 --> 02:02:05,390
 一万金克郎  一万?
 Ten thousand gold crowns.  Ten thousand?

1111
02:02:05,460 --> 02:02:07,120
真不少啊
That's a lot.

1112
02:02:07,200 --> 02:02:11,220
阁下 这件棘手的谈判就由您负责吧
Your Grace, I place you in charge of this very delicate negotiation.

1113
02:02:26,520 --> 02:02:29,040
收拾好 你要走了
Get yourself ready. You're leaving.

1114
02:02:32,150 --> 02:02:33,750
你是谁?
Who are you?

1115
02:02:33,820 --> 02:02:36,920
皮埃尔·戈尚 博韦的主教
Pierre Cauchon, bishop of Beauvais.

1116
02:02:36,990 --> 02:02:40,760
既然在我的教区抓获了你 那你的审判由我负责
As you were captured in my diocese, the duty to conduct the trial falls upon me.

1117
02:02:41,960 --> 02:02:45,660
审判? 什么审判?
Trial? What trial?

1118
02:02:45,740 --> 02:02:49,430
审判你 贞德 异端邪说罪
Your trial,Jeanne, on a charge of heresy.

1119
02:02:52,440 --> 02:02:54,240
可是我的国王...
But my king...

1120
02:02:55,980 --> 02:02:58,140
他没有付我的赎金?
Didn't he pay my ransom?

1121
02:02:58,210 --> 02:03:01,010
似乎英国人比法国人更关心你
It seems the English care more about you than the French.

1122
02:03:01,080 --> 02:03:03,610
 英国人?  是啊
 The English?  Yes.

1123
02:03:03,690 --> 02:03:05,480
英国人付了你的赎金
They paid your ransom.

1124
02:03:05,550 --> 02:03:09,650
明天你就被送到他们在鲁昂的城堡
Tomorrow you'll be transferred to their great castle at Rouen.

1125
02:04:10,850 --> 02:04:14,880
虔诚的英格兰及法兰西国王亨利六世...
Our serene and Christian king, Henry VI, king of England and France...

1126
02:04:14,960 --> 02:04:18,320
把这个女孩交给我们 控告她异端邪说罪...
has placed this girl in our hands, accused of heretical deeds...

1127
02:04:18,390 --> 02:04:20,760
为了确保审判忠实
to be tried in a matter of faith.

1128
02:04:20,830 --> 02:04:23,130
请你手持福音...
Take the Holy Gospels in your hand...

1129
02:04:23,200 --> 02:04:26,860
发誓不论回答什么都要诚实
and swear to tell the truth regarding anything you may be asked.

1130
02:04:28,270 --> 02:04:32,640
我不知道你要问我什么 可能有些我不想回答
I don't know what you will ask me. You may ask things I won't want to answer.

1131
02:04:32,710 --> 02:04:35,840
你要发誓对问你的一切 都要诚实回答
You will swear to tell the truth about everything you are asked.

1132
02:04:35,910 --> 02:04:40,310
我愿意诚恳地诉说一切
I will willingly tell the truth about all Earthly things.

1133
02:04:40,380 --> 02:04:44,610
可遵照我得到的启示 我只给我的国王一个人讲
But as to my revelations, I've told no one except my king...

1134
02:04:45,820 --> 02:04:48,760
查尔斯七世 法兰西唯一的国王
Charles VII, the one and only king of France.

1135
02:04:50,960 --> 02:04:53,330
你必须发誓
You must take the oath.

1136
02:04:53,400 --> 02:04:56,990
就算是国王也不准拒绝发誓
Not even a king would refuse to take an oath in a matter of faith.

1137
02:04:57,070 --> 02:04:59,760
可以告诉你的 我自然会讲
I will tell you all that I'm allowed to tell you.

1138
02:05:01,100 --> 02:05:03,040
可至于其他的...
But as for the rest...

1139
02:05:03,110 --> 02:05:06,470
就算你杀了我 我也不会说的
even if you threatened to cut off my head, I won't tell you.

1140
02:05:11,950 --> 02:05:16,250
那先告诉我们你的名字 这总可以说吧
Begin by telling us your name, assuming you're allowed to tell us that much.

1141
02:05:18,050 --> 02:05:19,820
我叫贞德
My name is Jeanne.

1142
02:05:21,190 --> 02:05:24,750
我的小十字架被拿走了 可以还给我吗?
My little cross was taken from me. May I have it back?

1143
02:05:24,830 --> 02:05:27,990
那你必须先更合作些
Show us a little more cooperation first.

1144
02:05:28,060 --> 02:05:30,220
你出生于何处?
Where were you born?

1145
02:05:30,300 --> 02:05:32,860
一个叫栋雷米的村子
In a village called Domremy.

1146
02:05:32,940 --> 02:05:34,870
你多大了?
How old are you?

1147
02:05:34,940 --> 02:05:37,300
十九吧 差不多
Nineteen, or thereabouts.

1148
02:05:37,370 --> 02:05:39,270
你入教了吗?
Were you baptized?

1149
02:05:40,440 --> 02:05:43,040
 是的  那背诵一下天主经
 Yes.  Recite our Lord's Prayer.

1150
02:05:44,910 --> 02:05:48,440
除非你听我做忏悔
Not unless you hear my confession.

1151
02:05:52,390 --> 02:05:54,690
你给我听好了
Listen to me very carefully.

1152
02:05:54,760 --> 02:05:57,190
我们都是虔诚的人...
We are all men of faith...

1153
02:05:57,260 --> 02:06:01,720
我们会诚心的拯救你和你的灵魂...
and we shall earnestly strive for the salvation of your body and your soul...

1154
02:06:01,800 --> 02:06:06,500
教堂的大门永远向迷途知返的人敞开
in the name of our Church who never closes arms to those who return to her.

1155
02:06:06,570 --> 02:06:08,590
可如果你不承认我们的评判和权威...
But we cannot help you...

1156
02:06:08,670 --> 02:06:11,470
我们就无法帮助你
unless you submit to our learned judgment and authority.

1157
02:06:11,540 --> 02:06:14,740
这是给你的提醒...
Take heed of this charitable admonition...

1158
02:06:14,810 --> 02:06:16,940
如果你坚持拒绝我们的帮助...
for if you persist in refusing our help...

1159
02:06:17,010 --> 02:06:21,570
那我们就不得不把你交给其他部门处理了
we shall have no choice but to abandon you to the secular powers.

1160
02:06:21,650 --> 02:06:24,520
等待你的惩罚我想你很清楚
And I think you know well enough the punishment that would await you.

1161
02:06:30,130 --> 02:06:32,090
现在...
Now...

1162
02:06:32,160 --> 02:06:35,190
你愿意背诵一下天主经吗?
will you please recite our Lord's Prayer?

1163
02:06:37,830 --> 02:06:40,500
除非你听我做忏悔
Not unless you hear my confession.

1164
02:06:43,440 --> 02:06:48,240
当心 拒绝承认审判对你没有好处的
Be careful. You aren't helping yourself by refusing to submit to our judgment.

1165
02:06:48,310 --> 02:06:50,240
你们...
You...

1166
02:06:50,310 --> 02:06:53,280
声称是审判我的人 你们才该当心!
who claim to be my judges, you be careful!

1167
02:06:54,350 --> 02:06:56,980
早晚有一天你们也会遭到审判的
For you too one day will be judged.

1168
02:06:57,050 --> 02:06:58,680
卫兵 把她带走!
Guards, take the prisoner away!

1169
02:07:01,720 --> 02:07:03,890
 肃静!  她是巫婆!
 Silence!  Sorceress!

1170
02:07:03,960 --> 02:07:07,330
肃静! 肃静!
Silence! Clear the room!

1171
02:07:07,400 --> 02:07:10,060
肃静!
Clear the room!

1172
02:07:11,870 --> 02:07:16,430
以后我们要秘密调查 避免受到民众的压力
In future, we should conduct inquiries privately, away from public pressure.

1173
02:07:16,510 --> 02:07:19,800
英国人愿意烧死她就烧死她吧 为什么要把我们扯进来呢?
Let the English burn her if they want. Why does it have to involve us?

1174
02:07:19,880 --> 02:07:23,210
因为找出她异端的罪证是我们的职责
Because it's our duty to root out heresy wherever we find it.

1175
02:07:25,310 --> 02:07:26,470
文森特神父
Father Vincente.

1176
02:07:28,520 --> 02:07:30,820
您是我们当中最受人尊敬的人 您怎么看?
You're the most venerable among us. What do you think?

1177
02:07:30,890 --> 02:07:33,410
我认为这个审判是假冒的...
I think this trial is a masquerade...

1178
02:07:33,490 --> 02:07:36,050
我不会再参与了
and I won't be part of it anymore.

1179
02:07:36,130 --> 02:07:39,620
我乐意作她的审判 而不是刽子手
I'm willing to be her judge, but not her executioner.

1180
02:07:39,700 --> 02:07:41,630
这一点我会保证
That's what I'm trying to ensure.

1181
02:07:44,830 --> 02:07:50,470
判决是在审判结束时下的 戈尚 不是在开始
The verdict comes at the end of a trial, Cauchon. Not at the beginning.

1182
02:07:52,240 --> 02:07:54,400
我要回罗马去...
I am going back to Rome...

1183
02:07:54,480 --> 02:07:57,640
向教皇报告此事
to give my report to our Holy Father, the Pope.

1184
02:08:00,150 --> 02:08:04,680
这太荒谬了 我倒成了被审判的人
This is ridiculous. Now I'm the one who's on trial and being judged.

1185
02:08:04,750 --> 02:08:06,810
 把他扣起来  你们干什么?
 Arrest him.  What are you doing?

1186
02:08:06,890 --> 02:08:10,150
这是教会法庭 你们无权这么做
This is an ecclesiastical court. You've no right to do this.

1187
02:08:10,230 --> 02:08:12,460
这是在英国的领地
This is English territory.

1188
02:08:12,530 --> 02:08:14,550
我有权做任何事
I have the right to do anything.

1189
02:08:14,630 --> 02:08:16,830
明白了吗?
Is that clear?

1190
02:08:32,850 --> 02:08:34,510
天上的神啊...
Our Father who art in heaven...

1191
02:08:34,580 --> 02:08:36,550
请在天堂...
Thy kingdom come...

1192
02:08:41,520 --> 02:08:43,750
宽恕我们...宽恕他们...
Forgive us...Forgive them...

1193
02:08:43,830 --> 02:08:47,060
宽恕他们吧 宽恕我们吧 宽恕他们吧
Forgive them, then forgive us. Forgive them.

1194
02:08:47,130 --> 02:08:48,530
你这是在念叨什么?
Why were you yelling?

1195
02:08:53,540 --> 02:08:57,130
你在这儿做什么? 你不能待在这里! 走开!
What are you doing here? You can't stay here! Go away!

1196
02:08:57,210 --> 02:08:59,970
为什么? 你在等其他人吗?
Why? Are you waiting for someone else?

1197
02:09:01,080 --> 02:09:02,170
是的
Yes.

1198
02:09:02,910 --> 02:09:05,640
 谁?  我的幻觉
 Who?  My visions.

1199
02:09:05,710 --> 02:09:07,310
你的幻觉
Your visions.

1200
02:09:08,520 --> 02:09:10,510
他们会来这里见你?
They're going to visit you in here?

1201
02:09:10,590 --> 02:09:13,490
是的 我是这么恳求的
Yes. That's what I pray for.

1202
02:09:14,290 --> 02:09:17,550
我倒想看看 介意我坐在这边吗?
I want to see that. Do you mind if I stay on the side here?

1203
02:09:17,630 --> 02:09:18,850
 我不会打扰你的  不行!
 I won't bother you.  No!

1204
02:09:20,460 --> 02:09:22,090
不行! 你不能待在这里!
No, you can't! You can't!

1205
02:09:22,160 --> 02:09:24,160
 否则他们就不会来了  为什么不会?
 Or else they won't come.  Why won't they?

1206
02:09:24,230 --> 02:09:26,430
因为我一定要一个人
Because I have to be alone.

1207
02:09:26,500 --> 02:09:30,200
算了 反正他们不会来的
Oh. They won't come anyway.

1208
02:09:31,110 --> 02:09:33,940
 你什么意思 他们不会来吗?  他们为什么来呢?
 What do you mean, they won't come?  Why would they?

1209
02:09:35,140 --> 02:09:38,170
因为我一直对上帝很忠诚啊...
Because I've always been faithful to God...

1210
02:09:38,250 --> 02:09:40,110
他所有的指示我都照做了...
and I've followed everything He's ever said...

1211
02:09:40,180 --> 02:09:42,340
他要求的事我都做到了
and I've done everything He's ever asked me to do.

1212
02:09:42,420 --> 02:09:44,210
上帝要你做事情?
God asked you to do something?

1213
02:09:48,560 --> 02:09:50,390
是的 很多事
Yes, lots of things.

1214
02:09:50,460 --> 02:09:53,720
你的意思是 上帝他说...
You mean, God said...

1215
02:09:53,800 --> 02:09:55,590
"贞德 我需要你"?
"I need you,Jeanne"?

1216
02:09:58,330 --> 02:10:01,130
可他给了我许多征兆
But He's sent me signs.

1217
02:10:02,910 --> 02:10:05,470
征兆? 什么征兆?
Signs? What signs?

1218
02:10:07,680 --> 02:10:09,410
风 风
The wind. The wind.

1219
02:10:13,920 --> 02:10:14,880
风
Wind.

1220
02:10:14,950 --> 02:10:17,940
还有云 钟声
And the clouds. Ringing.

1221
02:10:20,620 --> 02:10:22,250
钟声 云
Ringing cloud.

1222
02:10:23,230 --> 02:10:25,220
跳舞 还有跳舞
The dance. The dance.

1223
02:10:39,810 --> 02:10:42,780
剑 田野里的剑
The sword. The sword lying in the field.

1224
02:10:42,840 --> 02:10:44,510
那就是征兆
That was a sign.

1225
02:10:44,580 --> 02:10:48,020
不 那只是田野里的一把剑
No. That was a sword in a field.

1226
02:10:49,220 --> 02:10:52,090
不 不 那是征兆
No. No. That was a sign.

1227
02:10:52,150 --> 02:10:55,090
不 那只是田野里的一把剑
No, that was a sword in a field.

1228
02:10:55,160 --> 02:10:59,220
可它不会自己跑到那里的
It can't just get there by itself. It can't.

1229
02:10:59,290 --> 02:11:02,290
剑不会自己跑到那里的
A sword just doesn't get there by itself.

1230
02:11:02,360 --> 02:11:07,100
没错 任何事都会有无数可能 你为何非取其中的一种呢?
True. Every event has an infinite number of causes, so why pick one?

1231
02:11:07,170 --> 02:11:09,640
要在田野里出现剑有很多途径
There are many ways a sword might find itself in a field.

1232
02:11:14,840 --> 02:11:18,610
看来这种解释不错 那这种呢?
Seems a perfectly valid explanation, but how about this one?

1233
02:11:24,650 --> 02:11:26,640
也不错 还有其他可能
Then again, there are other possibilities.

1234
02:11:31,460 --> 02:11:32,650
还有更快的
Or even faster.

1235
02:11:36,230 --> 02:11:39,220
还没有算其它的
And that's without counting the inexplicable.

1236
02:11:41,600 --> 02:11:45,840
有这么多可能 你却偏偏选这个
Yet from an infinite number of possibilities, you had to pick this one.

1237
02:11:59,550 --> 02:12:03,350
你看到的不是真相 贞德
You didn't see what was,Jeanne.

1238
02:12:03,430 --> 02:12:06,660
你看到的是你想要看的罢了
You saw what you wanted to see.

1239
02:12:22,940 --> 02:12:26,680
你说有声音对你说话...
This voice that you say appears to you...

1240
02:12:26,750 --> 02:12:30,840
是天使说的还是圣人说的 或者是上帝亲自说的?
is it an angel or a saint, or does it come from God?

1241
02:12:30,920 --> 02:12:35,360
我不再跟你说那些了
I won't tell you any more about that.

1242
02:12:35,420 --> 02:12:37,920
不是怕回答你 是怕惹怒上帝
I'm more afraid of displeasing Him than not answering you.

1243
02:12:37,990 --> 02:12:42,860
你怕说实话会惹怒上帝?
You're afraid of displeasing God by telling the truth?

1244
02:12:42,930 --> 02:12:46,300
难道上帝禁止你说实话?
Did God forbid you to tell the truth?

1245
02:12:46,370 --> 02:12:50,300
我只跟法国国王说 不是你
My revelations were for the king of France, not for you.

1246
02:12:52,370 --> 02:12:54,930
你第一眼看见国王时...
When you saw your king for the first time...

1247
02:12:55,010 --> 02:12:57,410
他头顶上有天使在飞吗?
was there an angel over his head?

1248
02:12:57,480 --> 02:12:59,240
可能有 我没有看见
If there was one, I did not see it.

1249
02:12:59,310 --> 02:13:02,280
没有任何证明 你的国王凭什么相信你?
Why did your king believe in you without any proof?

1250
02:13:03,290 --> 02:13:04,880
你问他去
Go ask him yourself.

1251
02:13:18,530 --> 02:13:19,560
晚饭
Dinner.

1252
02:13:36,050 --> 02:13:39,320
你被抓时 是骑着马吗?
When you were taken prisoner, did you have a horse?

1253
02:13:39,390 --> 02:13:42,820
是的 有一半战马血统 黑色的
Yes. A half steed. Black.

1254
02:13:42,890 --> 02:13:45,450
 马是谁给你的?  国王
 Who gave you that horse?  My king.

1255
02:13:45,530 --> 02:13:47,930
他给了你多少?
How many did he give you?

1256
02:13:50,100 --> 02:13:52,570
五匹战马...
Five steeds...

1257
02:13:52,630 --> 02:13:55,300
还有几匹一般的马
and a few hackneys.

1258
02:13:55,370 --> 02:13:58,530
不少啊 赶上侯爵们了 真是光荣啊
As much as for a lord. What an honor.

1259
02:13:58,610 --> 02:14:01,200
除了这些马 国王还有没有给你其他财富?
Did your king give you other wealth apart from those horses?

1260
02:14:03,250 --> 02:14:06,610
那些给你的衣服呢?
What about all those dresses you were given?

1261
02:14:06,680 --> 02:14:08,150
是丝绸的 对吗?
Silk dresses, weren't they?

1262
02:14:09,350 --> 02:14:10,440
是的
Yes.

1263
02:14:10,520 --> 02:14:13,110
是给过我一些
Yes, I was given a few.

1264
02:14:13,190 --> 02:14:16,950
可我从没有时间穿
But I never had time to wear them.

1265
02:14:17,030 --> 02:14:20,520
作为一个农民来说算很富有了 你有什么好说的?
Still, pretty wealthy for a peasant girl, wouldn't you say?

1266
02:14:23,030 --> 02:14:27,060
作为上帝的仆人 你看来也很富有 你有什么好说?
You look pretty wealthy for a servant of God, wouldn't you say?

1267
02:14:32,510 --> 02:14:34,700
是你带人进攻巴黎的 是吗?
You launched an attack on Paris, didn't you?

1268
02:14:34,780 --> 02:14:36,800
是我
I tried to.

1269
02:14:36,880 --> 02:14:39,040
你有没有以上帝的名义...
And didn't you order the citizens of Paris to surrender the city...

1270
02:14:39,110 --> 02:14:40,480
命令巴黎的百姓献城投降?
in the name of the King of Heaven?

1271
02:14:40,550 --> 02:14:44,750
不 我说 "向法兰西国王投降吧"
No. I said, "Surrender in the name of the king of France."

1272
02:14:44,820 --> 02:14:47,410
证据上不是这么写的
That is not what is written in the evidence.

1273
02:14:49,090 --> 02:14:50,490
你自己看
Look yourself.

1274
02:14:50,560 --> 02:14:53,760
我不识字
I can't read.

1275
02:14:55,360 --> 02:14:57,850
我忘了
Yes, I forgot.

1276
02:14:57,930 --> 02:15:01,990
上帝竟然派了个不识字的使者来完成这么重要的使命
God sent us an illiterate peasant to carry out such an important mission.

1277
02:15:02,070 --> 02:15:04,230
你认为上帝这么做 对吗?
Do you think that God made the right decision?

1278
02:15:04,310 --> 02:15:08,800
让一个无知的女孩来拯救法国?
To take an ignorant girl to save the kingdom of France?

1279
02:15:08,880 --> 02:15:10,540
这只有上帝能回答
I leave that answer to God.

1280
02:15:15,320 --> 02:15:17,050
靠!
Fuck!

1281
02:15:17,120 --> 02:15:19,110
冷静一下 大人 求你了
Calm down, my lord. I beg you.

1282
02:15:19,190 --> 02:15:22,250
我现在是整个朝廷的笑柄 我怎么冷静得下来?
How can I when I'm made the laughingstock of the whole court?

1283
02:15:22,320 --> 02:15:24,690
你也看见了 这女孩对付百姓很有一套...
You've seen how it is. This girl has a way with people...

1284
02:15:24,760 --> 02:15:26,920
可我们每天都还是有进展的
but we're making progress every day.

1285
02:15:27,000 --> 02:15:30,950
只要这娘们还活着 我们军队就拒绝打仗 你明白么?
As long as that bitch remains alive, our armies refuse to fight. Understand?

1286
02:15:31,030 --> 02:15:32,830
他们要确定上帝是站在我们这边
They need proof that God is on their side.

1287
02:15:32,900 --> 02:15:35,700
我们不能烧死她 你们才能那么做
It's not for us to burn her. That's your prerogative.

1288
02:15:35,770 --> 02:15:37,570
你们的任务就是找出她的罪过!
And it's your prerogative to find her guilty!

1289
02:15:37,640 --> 02:15:40,900
除非她承认亵渎了上帝 否则我们不能那么做
But we can't do that unless she admits to blasphemy.

1290
02:15:40,980 --> 02:15:42,500
你还等什么?
What are you waiting for?

1291
02:15:42,580 --> 02:15:45,880
这城堡里的刑具应有尽有 严刑拷打啊!
You've got a castle full of racks, ropes and pulleys. Torture the bitch!

1292
02:15:45,950 --> 02:15:48,850
那样她什么都不会说的
You'll never get anything out of her that way.

1293
02:15:48,920 --> 02:15:51,680
还有...
And besides...

1294
02:15:51,750 --> 02:15:56,920
我的几个同僚...已经害怕了
you must realize that several of my colleagues are, well, scared.

1295
02:15:56,990 --> 02:15:59,760
害怕? 害怕一个女孩?
Scared? Of a girl?

1296
02:15:59,830 --> 02:16:02,460
害怕犯错误
Scared to make a mistake.

1297
02:16:02,530 --> 02:16:04,760
万一她是对的呢
Suppose she's right.

1298
02:16:04,830 --> 02:16:07,300
万一她真是上帝派来的呢
Suppose she has been sent by God.

1299
02:16:11,770 --> 02:16:16,510
 你站在谁那边 戈尚?  我只站在教会这边
 Who's side are you on, Cauchon?  I'm on the side of Holy Mother Church.

1300
02:16:17,550 --> 02:16:19,640
你有剑吗?
Do you have a sword?

1301
02:16:21,120 --> 02:16:23,280
 有不少  你不是还常带着旗吗?
 Quite a few.  Didn't you also carry a banner?

1302
02:16:24,820 --> 02:16:25,840
是的
Yes.

1303
02:16:25,920 --> 02:16:29,150
你更喜欢哪个? 旗还是剑?
Which do you prefer? Your banner or your sword?

1304
02:16:29,220 --> 02:16:31,750
我绝对是喜欢我的旗
I was 40 times more fond of my banner.

1305
02:16:31,830 --> 02:16:34,760
为什么? 它有什么特殊的价值或者力量?
Why? Did it have some particular value or power?

1306
02:16:37,200 --> 02:16:39,720
只是...
It's just...

1307
02:16:39,800 --> 02:16:42,600
 剑是武器  所以呢?
 A sword is a weapon.  And?

1308
02:16:43,710 --> 02:16:47,870
所以 我更喜欢旗
And so, I prefer my banner.

1309
02:16:47,940 --> 02:16:49,070
为什么?
Why?

1310
02:16:49,140 --> 02:16:52,110
我不想杀人
To avoid killing anyone.

1311
02:16:52,180 --> 02:16:55,270
你是说如果你没有一直拿着旗的话...
Are you saying if you'd not been carrying your banner...

1312
02:16:55,350 --> 02:16:56,870
你就会杀更多的人?
you'd have killed more people?

1313
02:17:01,190 --> 02:17:03,160
不是这个意思 我从没有杀过人
Of course not. I never killed anyone.

1314
02:17:03,220 --> 02:17:05,990
拿剑时杀人的欲望...
Then perhaps the temptation...

1315
02:17:06,060 --> 02:17:08,150
可能就会更强烈吧...
to kill would have been stronger...

1316
02:17:08,230 --> 02:17:10,130
非常强烈
too strong, perhaps.

1317
02:17:11,670 --> 02:17:13,690
我警告过英国人 让他们撤军
I warned the English to go back home.

1318
02:17:13,770 --> 02:17:16,290
我请求他们不要与我们为敌 他们知道我...
I begged them not to force us to fight. They knew that I...

1319
02:17:16,370 --> 02:17:18,840
我们有很多证人可以证明...
We have numerous witnesses who can confirm...

1320
02:17:18,910 --> 02:17:20,900
你不是一直拿着那面旗的
you were not always carrying your banner.

1321
02:17:25,110 --> 02:17:26,840
是的 可能吧
Yes, perhaps.

1322
02:17:26,920 --> 02:17:29,180
有时你只拿着你的剑
Sometimes you were carrying just your sword.

1323
02:17:30,920 --> 02:17:32,750
是的 我不清楚
Yes. I don't know.

1324
02:17:32,820 --> 02:17:34,950
你有没有用过手中的剑呢?
Did you use the sword you held in your hand?

1325
02:17:35,020 --> 02:17:37,180
是的 我用过...我把它高高举起...
Yes, I used it...I held it up...

1326
02:17:37,260 --> 02:17:40,660
你是把剑高高举起 然后就像这样挥动吧!
You held up your sword and flourished it about like this!

1327
02:17:40,730 --> 02:17:41,750
我不记得了
I don't remember.

1328
02:17:41,830 --> 02:17:44,800
所以你在战场上 手持利剑...
So, you were on the battlefield with your sword in your hand...

1329
02:17:44,870 --> 02:17:47,890
高高的挥舞...
waving it above your head, charging against the enemy...

1330
02:17:47,970 --> 02:17:50,440
为了保全性命大声叫嚷着同敌人战斗...
screaming at the enemy, fighting for your life...

1331
02:17:50,510 --> 02:17:52,300
而你却要我们相信...
and you expect us to believe...

1332
02:17:52,370 --> 02:17:55,900
在这么激烈的过程中...
that in the middle of all this excitement...

1333
02:17:55,980 --> 02:18:00,240
你没杀过一个人
you never killed anyone.

1334
02:18:00,320 --> 02:18:03,770
是 我没杀过人
No. I never killed anyone.

1335
02:18:05,820 --> 02:18:07,520
我不相信 你撒谎了
I can't believe you can lie like that.

1336
02:18:07,590 --> 02:18:10,850
我没说谎 没说谎 别烦我 我不记得了
I'm not lying. I'm not lying. Leave me alone. I can't remember.

1337
02:18:10,930 --> 02:18:14,120
 我没杀过人 我不记得了  那我来帮你回忆一下
 I didn't kill anyone. I can't remember.  Let me help your memory.

1338
02:18:14,760 --> 02:18:17,530
我不想听了 别烦我 我没有杀那个人
I don't want to hear any more. Leave me alone. I didn't kill that man.

1339
02:18:17,600 --> 02:18:19,030
别烦我!
Leave me alone!

1340
02:18:19,100 --> 02:18:21,970
停下 停下 我不记得了
Stop. Stop. I can't remember.

1341
02:18:22,040 --> 02:18:26,300
战斗昏天暗地的 我只是尽可能的保护好自己
The battles were so confusing. I was only defending myself as best I could.

1342
02:18:26,370 --> 02:18:30,400
烟火弥漫 叫喊连天 我又四面受敌
There was so much dust, smoke and noise. I was being attacked on all sides.

1343
02:18:30,480 --> 02:18:33,280
可能我是还击了
So maybe perhaps I fought back.

1344
02:18:33,350 --> 02:18:36,370
 可那只是为了保护自己  看来你想起来了
 But it was only to defend myself.  So your memory's coming back.

1345
02:18:36,450 --> 02:18:38,420
 是的  很好
 Yes.  Good.

1346
02:18:38,490 --> 02:18:42,720
那你告诉我为什么上帝会让战争爆发呢
Now, you tell me why God let all those battles happen in the first place.

1347
02:18:42,790 --> 02:18:44,350
他如此的强大 你还说...
He's so powerful. You said...

1348
02:18:44,430 --> 02:18:46,720
"他创造万物 是天地之主"
" He's the creator of heaven and Earth, the source of all life."

1349
02:18:46,800 --> 02:18:50,060
他可以轻易地阻止 那些流血和不幸的发生
He could easily have stopped all that blood and misery.

1350
02:18:50,130 --> 02:18:51,100
为什么没这么做?
Why didn't He...

1351
02:18:51,170 --> 02:18:54,160
是他在散播流血和不幸吗?
Is He the one who spread all that blood and misery?

1352
02:18:54,240 --> 02:18:56,400
 是他吗?  不是 可他应该阻止这一切的
 Is He?  No. But He could have stopped it.

1353
02:18:56,470 --> 02:18:59,270
看到我们以他的名义...互相残杀...
What, did he get pleasure...pleasure...

1354
02:18:59,340 --> 02:19:02,970
他感到很愉悦吗?
pleasure from watching us killing each other in His name?

1355
02:19:03,040 --> 02:19:05,540
以他的名义?
In His name?

1356
02:19:05,610 --> 02:19:08,880
是以他的名义 我们以他的名义互相战斗和杀戮...
In His name. We fought and killed in His name...

1357
02:19:08,950 --> 02:19:11,080
 以上帝的名义  真的吗?
 the King of Heaven.  Really?

1358
02:19:11,150 --> 02:19:13,780
所有爱我的人哪 跟我冲啊!
Let all those who love me follow me!

1359
02:19:13,860 --> 02:19:16,480
"所有爱我的人 跟我冲!"
"Let all who love me follow me!"

1360
02:19:16,560 --> 02:19:19,120
哪里提到上帝了?
Where does God get mentioned?

1361
02:19:19,190 --> 02:19:21,590
算了吧 贞德
Come on,Jeanne.

1362
02:19:21,660 --> 02:19:23,460
诚实些吧
Be honest.

1363
02:19:23,530 --> 02:19:26,360
你是为你自己而战 以自己的名义而战
You fought for yourself. In your name.

1364
02:19:26,430 --> 02:19:28,490
不是的!
No!

1365
02:19:28,570 --> 02:19:30,940
我只是尽可能的在保护自己
I was defending myself as best as I could.

1366
02:19:31,010 --> 02:19:33,800
保护自己是没有错的 不是吗?
Everyone has the right to defend themselves, don't they?

1367
02:19:33,880 --> 02:19:36,240
是的 应该这样! 难道我要让自己去死吗?
Yes, they do! Should I have let myself get killed?

1368
02:19:36,310 --> 02:19:37,940
 要那样吗?  不 你做的很好
 Is that it?  No. You did fine.

1369
02:19:38,010 --> 02:19:39,980
甚至说做的很棒
I'd even say well done.

1370
02:19:40,050 --> 02:19:42,240
事实上...
As a matter of fact...

1371
02:19:42,320 --> 02:19:45,480
那你认为那些被你杀的人也是罪有应得了?
most of the ones you killed probably deserved it, don't you think?

1372
02:19:49,020 --> 02:19:51,860
我从来不认为杀戮能换来和平
I never thought killing each other would bring about any peace.

1373
02:19:51,930 --> 02:19:52,820
我同意
I agree.

1374
02:19:52,890 --> 02:19:55,390
只有跟英国人战斗才能换来和平
Peace will only be got from the English at the end of a lance.

1375
02:19:55,460 --> 02:19:58,560
我不同意 你的想法为什么变来变去呢?
I don't agree. Why do you keep changing your mind all the time?

1376
02:20:00,300 --> 02:20:02,460
是你 为什么...
You. Why...

1377
02:20:02,540 --> 02:20:05,170
你为什么要这么对我?
Why are you doing this to me?

1378
02:20:05,240 --> 02:20:07,400
伤害我 你感到很快乐吗?
Do you get pleasure from hurting me?

1379
02:20:07,480 --> 02:20:11,380
快乐 真是个难以定义的词汇
Pleasure. That's a difficult word to define.

1380
02:20:13,150 --> 02:20:17,380
痛苦何时结束? 快乐何时开始? 你的快乐是何时开始的?
When does pain end and pleasure begin? When did your pleasure begin?

1381
02:20:17,450 --> 02:20:21,650
是你手持利剑的时候吗?
With that sword in your hand?

1382
02:20:22,920 --> 02:20:26,120
伤害其他人...
I never took pleasure...

1383
02:20:26,190 --> 02:20:28,660
我从不会感到快乐
in hurting anyone.

1384
02:20:29,700 --> 02:20:31,190
真的吗?
Really?

1385
02:20:56,290 --> 02:21:00,090
放我走吧 放我走吧
Set me free. Set me free.

1386
02:21:00,160 --> 02:21:01,790
会的 贞德
You will be,Jeanne.

1387
02:21:02,930 --> 02:21:04,870
会的
You will be.

1388
02:21:26,050 --> 02:21:28,580
贞德 我最亲爱的教友...
Jeanne, my very dear friend in Christ...

1389
02:21:28,660 --> 02:21:30,590
所有审判员
we, your judges and assessors...

1390
02:21:30,660 --> 02:21:33,250
渴望得出一个真实公正的判决...
desirous of reaching a true and lawful verdict...

1391
02:21:33,330 --> 02:21:36,730
所以把你的审判发到巴黎大学...
submitted a transcript of your trial to the University of Paris...

1392
02:21:36,800 --> 02:21:38,060
征求了他们的意见
to attain their opinion.

1393
02:21:38,130 --> 02:21:40,600
经过慎重考虑...
After careful consideration...

1394
02:21:40,670 --> 02:21:42,690
学者们跟我们一致认定...
the learned scholars have concluded with us...

1395
02:21:42,770 --> 02:21:46,400
你已犯下多项重大罪行
that you have committed many grievous sins.

1396
02:21:46,470 --> 02:21:48,970
现在我要你仔细听他们的意见...
I ask you now to listen most carefully...

1397
02:21:49,040 --> 02:21:51,980
具体如下
to their opinion, as detailed in these articles.

1398
02:21:54,850 --> 02:21:56,510
罪行一
Article One.

1399
02:21:56,580 --> 02:22:00,750
你自称是上帝命令你穿男人的衣服...
You said that by God's command you have continually worn men's clothes...

1400
02:22:00,820 --> 02:22:03,120
剪成男人的短发...
and that you have also worn your hair short...

1401
02:22:03,190 --> 02:22:06,350
无法将你同你的敌人分辨出来
with nothing to distinguish you from the soldiers with whom you fought.

1402
02:22:10,000 --> 02:22:12,730
请不要遗弃我
Don't abandon me. Please.

1403
02:22:14,800 --> 02:22:17,970
您在哪里?
Where are You?

1404
02:22:18,040 --> 02:22:20,060
您在哪里啊?
Where are You? Please.

1405
02:22:24,110 --> 02:22:27,240
这就是您想要的吗?
Is this what You want?

1406
02:22:28,680 --> 02:22:31,380
您想要我...
You want me to...

1407
02:22:31,450 --> 02:22:33,850
在还没有...
to burn...

1408
02:22:33,920 --> 02:22:35,910
做忏悔的情况下...
without...

1409
02:22:35,990 --> 02:22:38,550
就被烧死吗?
being confessed?

1410
02:22:38,630 --> 02:22:41,690
最后 罪行十二
Finally, Article 1 2.

1411
02:22:41,760 --> 02:22:44,130
声称不愿服从...
You have said that you are not willing to submit yourself...

1412
02:22:44,200 --> 02:22:47,790
教会法庭的审判 只服从上帝
to the judgment of the church militant, but only to God.

1413
02:22:47,870 --> 02:22:49,800
对于这一点 学者们认为...
As to this article, the scholars say...

1414
02:22:49,870 --> 02:22:52,640
你藐视教会的权威
that you have no comprehension of the authority of the Church.

1415
02:22:52,710 --> 02:22:55,730
在信仰上你已误入歧途...
That you have perniciously erred in the faith of God...

1416
02:22:55,810 --> 02:22:59,470
追随迷信 偏离信仰...
and you are a child of superstition, a wanderer from the faith...

1417
02:22:59,550 --> 02:23:03,040
祈求和崇拜魔鬼...
an invoker of demons, an idolater...

1418
02:23:03,120 --> 02:23:05,050
是个异端邪说者
and a heretic.

1419
02:23:16,060 --> 02:23:19,630
我们再一次诚恳地劝告你...
We once again admonish, beg and exalt you...

1420
02:23:19,700 --> 02:23:23,260
放弃你错误的信仰吧...
to cast out and recant your erroneous beliefs...

1421
02:23:23,340 --> 02:23:26,360
在悔过书上签名吧
by signing this recantation.

1422
02:23:27,510 --> 02:23:28,500
签吧
Please.

1423
02:23:30,240 --> 02:23:32,270
如果教会...
If the Church...

1424
02:23:32,350 --> 02:23:35,610
想要我说...
wants me to say...

1425
02:23:35,680 --> 02:23:38,080
我所见的都是邪恶的...
that my visions are evil...

1426
02:23:38,150 --> 02:23:41,090
那我宁愿不相信这个教会
then I do not believe in this Church.

1427
02:23:46,260 --> 02:23:47,520
让你的人做准备
Perform your office.

1428
02:23:53,670 --> 02:23:55,100
等等
Wait.

1429
02:23:59,040 --> 02:24:02,340
贞德 我求你了 签吧
Jeanne, I beg of you, sign.

1430
02:24:02,410 --> 02:24:05,470
看在上帝的份上 你不明白吗? 我这是在救你啊
In God's name, don't you understand? I'm trying to save you.

1431
02:24:05,550 --> 02:24:08,040
我想要做忏悔
I want to be confessed.

1432
02:24:09,380 --> 02:24:11,780
签了这个 你愿意的话我帮你做忏悔
Sign this and I will confess you myself, if you want.

1433
02:24:11,850 --> 02:24:16,520
那我可以...
And may I...

1434
02:24:16,590 --> 02:24:19,490
我可以去做弥撒吗?
May I go to Mass?

1435
02:24:19,560 --> 02:24:21,620
只要你愿意
As often as you like.

1436
02:24:21,700 --> 02:24:24,460
为了上帝 签了吧
Now, for the love of God, sign.

1437
02:24:29,800 --> 02:24:33,040
签了吧 贞德 这能让你免于枷锁
Sign,Jeanne, and you'll be free of your chains.

1438
02:24:33,110 --> 02:24:35,510
免于火刑 贞德
Free of the fire,Jeanne.

1439
02:25:10,450 --> 02:25:12,110
谢谢
Thank you.

1440
02:25:15,680 --> 02:25:18,780
你知道你刚才签的是什么吗?
Do you know what you just signed?

1441
02:25:18,850 --> 02:25:21,480
你签字放弃了"他是存在的"这一信念
You just signed away His existence.

1442
02:25:22,990 --> 02:25:27,390
 我不是这个意思  你认为 他是个骗子
 I didn't mean to.  For you, He's a lie.

1443
02:25:29,200 --> 02:25:31,190
一切都是幻觉
An illusion.

1444
02:25:31,270 --> 02:25:33,460
不 不
No, no.

1445
02:25:33,530 --> 02:25:35,730
他说我可以做忏悔的
He told me that I would be confessed.

1446
02:25:36,640 --> 02:25:39,730
可你最终还是抛弃了他
In the end, it was you who abandoned Him.

1447
02:25:46,810 --> 02:25:49,310
 能再给我一下吗?  没什么好后悔的
 May I have that back, please?  You have nothing to regret.

1448
02:25:51,650 --> 02:25:54,210
还给我!
Give it back to me!

1449
02:25:54,290 --> 02:25:57,520
 还给我!  带她走!
 Give it back!  Take her away!

1450
02:26:02,230 --> 02:26:03,860
让她闭嘴!
Silence her!

1451
02:26:08,740 --> 02:26:10,900
给 她已经放弃了邪恶的信仰
There. She has recanted.

1452
02:26:10,970 --> 02:26:13,340
并且我们接受她的悔过...
And we accept her repentance...

1453
02:26:13,410 --> 02:26:16,870
教会的大门永远向迷途知返的人敞开
for the Church never closes her arms to those who would return to the fold.

1454
02:26:18,610 --> 02:26:22,810
是否处死她是你的事 不是我们的了
Now she's your martyr, not ours.

1455
02:26:49,110 --> 02:26:50,940
不要!
Please!

1456
02:26:57,450 --> 02:26:59,780
可以了
Enough.

1457
02:27:05,830 --> 02:27:07,920
给
Here.

1458
02:27:08,000 --> 02:27:11,800
想穿衣服的话就试试这身吧
If you want to get dressed, try these for size.

1459
02:27:18,040 --> 02:27:20,510
大主教
My lord bishop.

1460
02:27:30,250 --> 02:27:32,190
您自己看看
Come to see for yourself.

1461
02:27:32,250 --> 02:27:34,520
你来看
Well, take a look.

1462
02:27:39,660 --> 02:27:42,150
看见了吗? 又换成男人打扮了
You see? Dressed as a man again.

1463
02:27:42,230 --> 02:27:44,530
看来悔过不顶什么用啊?
Her touching repentance didn't last very long, did it?

1464
02:27:46,100 --> 02:27:50,870
桑利斯的主教刚巧路过 他目击了一切
The Bishop of Senlis was passing by and was on hand to witness her relapse.

1465
02:27:53,340 --> 02:27:56,440
凭空出现那衣服可真是奇迹啊?
And by what miracle did these clothes find their way in here?

1466
02:27:56,510 --> 02:27:58,640
那不是神迹 亲爱的戈尚
Not a miracle, my dear Cauchon.

1467
02:27:58,710 --> 02:28:00,980
是邪恶的魔咒
An evil spell.

1468
02:28:01,050 --> 02:28:04,380
那女孩是巫婆 明天要施以火刑
This girl is a witch, and tomorrow she will burn for it.

1469
02:28:06,320 --> 02:28:09,080
在菜市口做好准备
Have the stake prepared in the marketplace.

1470
02:28:24,110 --> 02:28:28,010
贞德 我真是不明白 你为什么要这么做?
Jeanne, I don't understand. Why did you do it?

1471
02:28:28,080 --> 02:28:29,870
 为什么啊?  那你呢
 Why?  And you.

1472
02:28:29,940 --> 02:28:32,140
为什么要撒谎?
Why did you lie?

1473
02:28:32,210 --> 02:28:34,010
你答应我要听我忏悔的
You promised to have me confessed.

1474
02:28:34,080 --> 02:28:36,980
我知道 可那是当时为了救你
I know. It was the only way to have you saved from the fire.

1475
02:28:37,050 --> 02:28:40,350
我要救的不是我的身躯
It's not my body I want to save.

1476
02:28:40,420 --> 02:28:42,080
而是我的灵魂
It's my soul.

1477
02:28:43,720 --> 02:28:46,450
我只求你一件事
I ask only one thing.

1478
02:28:46,530 --> 02:28:50,260
请听我做忏悔
Please, hear my confession.

1479
02:28:53,970 --> 02:28:57,800
不行 贞德 我不能听你做忏悔
I can't,Jeanne. I can't hear your confession.

1480
02:29:01,140 --> 02:29:03,080
非常抱歉
I'm very sorry.

1481
02:29:24,070 --> 02:29:25,970
你要做忏悔?
You want to confess?

1482
02:29:29,970 --> 02:29:32,460
我在听啊
I'm listening.

1483
02:29:32,540 --> 02:29:34,840
主啊 我有罪
I've committed sins, my Lord.

1484
02:29:38,050 --> 02:29:39,950
很多的罪
So many sins.

1485
02:29:43,420 --> 02:29:47,250
我看见了那么多的征兆
I saw so many signs.

1486
02:29:47,320 --> 02:29:49,380
那么多"征兆"
Many signs.

1487
02:29:51,330 --> 02:29:53,560
那些我想看见的
The ones I wanted to see.

1488
02:29:59,430 --> 02:30:01,900
我战斗...
I fought...

1489
02:30:05,110 --> 02:30:07,040
是因为仇恨...
out of revenge...

1490
02:30:09,980 --> 02:30:11,910
和绝望
and despair.

1491
02:30:19,090 --> 02:30:21,950
是我...
I was all the things...

1492
02:30:22,020 --> 02:30:25,980
让人们相信...
that people believe...

1493
02:30:26,060 --> 02:30:28,220
上帝允许他们...
they're allowed to be...

1494
02:30:28,300 --> 02:30:31,390
允许他们...
when they're fighting for...

1495
02:30:35,100 --> 02:30:36,630
为了理想而战
a cause.

1496
02:30:37,710 --> 02:30:39,040
为了理想
For a cause.

1497
02:30:41,380 --> 02:30:42,970
我很...
I was...

1498
02:30:45,380 --> 02:30:47,010
自豪...
proud...

1499
02:30:48,720 --> 02:30:50,310
也很...
and...

1500
02:30:53,320 --> 02:30:54,790
固执
stubborn.

1501
02:30:54,860 --> 02:30:56,450
自私
Selfish.

1502
02:30:57,790 --> 02:30:59,450
自私
Selfish.

1503
02:30:59,530 --> 02:31:02,190
是的 还有残忍
Yes. Cruel.

1504
02:31:05,300 --> 02:31:06,930
是的
Yes.

1505
02:31:07,000 --> 02:31:08,900
残忍
Cruel.

1506
02:31:11,040 --> 02:31:13,800
你做好准备了么?
You think you are ready now?

1507
02:31:18,080 --> 02:31:19,410
是的
Yes.

1508
02:31:21,320 --> 02:31:23,110
很好
Good.

